Feature:

1. Native application
2. Three views. the Main view, Location view, and the Details view.
3. The Main view can show the current weather and the short virsion of the 7 day forecast.
4. If the user click a special weather statement, the Details view should be displayed.
5. The Details ciew can show the respective details.
6. You can jump to the Location view from the Main view.
7. You can search the location by typing the city name.
8. you can scroll the list to click the city you want to see.
9. Users can come back to Main view directly by click the "back" button on Location view.

10. Bonus: Using graphics and visual elements

Wishlist:

1. Save the location that user has choosen.
